rComments: Prof Jones is a real gem! She is a true expert in the field and you can tell she is passionate about her work. She is very accommodating and wants all her students to do well. She makes discussion group classes fun with debates and other activities. Tophat is used for in class questions and attendance which I personally really liked.

Prof Jones was one of the nicest professors I've ever had-- she took the time to get to know every student's name in the whole class. She cared a lot about the material and worked hard to make her students interested in it as well. The lectures were extremely content heavy so make sure you take good notes and supplement them with your own research.
